Pumpkin Kid was on his way to his favorite corner store. He spotted a glimmering watering can in the window and he knew that he had to have it for his plants in the garden!
He went home and watered his plants right away!
Much to his amazement, the plants that he had just watered sprung to life right before him.
But where there's a new magic to be found like this, there is bound to be trouble afoot...

